<div class="reftext">1. So that I can work whilst swinging in my hammock, of course!<br />
2. And by available, I mean the user can search for a word, and get back *something*. Having to install Gnome help to be able to do a decent search of the KDE manuals, sounds kinda backwards, but hey, works!<!--reftxt-->
</div>
</div>
</div>
